{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "第一王子莱昂尼多率沙音和士兵们突然现身。\\n原来火焰都市发生的一切都是他所为！\\n莱昂尼多为求沉眠于红莲废道的魔神之力\\n而向更深处进发。\\n王子紧追自己的哥哥。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信徒",
            "context": "呜呜呜，救命……\\n救救……我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "哼，要是让你们继续活着，\\n就会动摇教义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "至少让你们不再痛苦，\\n去见伊莉雅吧！喝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "住手，沙音！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "到此为止了！\\n我们已经救出了其他信徒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "就算是遁入暗影的暗杀者，\\n在这种空旷之地被包围的话，\\n也无路可逃了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "呃，大意了。\\n没想到这么快就追上来了……\\n轻敌招致大患……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好了，乖乖地投降吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "人固有一死……如果无法寻回乐园，\\n至少让我死在这里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "等等。\\n别急着赴死，沙音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你的殒命之处不在这里。\\n我不许你草率对待自己的生命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "什么！？谁！？\\n这让人毛骨悚然的杀气……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01",
                "120080_01b",
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "帝国军！？\\n率领着士兵的那个男人是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "竟敢踏足我地盘里的废道，\\n何等愚蠢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "飞蛾扑火。看来不把你们连人带魂\\n统统烧尽，就不会明白自己的愚蠢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你是……\\n莱昂尼多哥哥！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "嚯，叫我哥哥的你是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我是第七王子，\\n尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "以前在王都见过几次……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不认识呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啥！？你居然说\\n不认识自己的亲生兄弟……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我兄弟多如牛毛，\\n还要我一个个全记住不成。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "能站在顶点、继承王位的只有一人。\\n除我之外，都不值一提。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这个人怎么回事……\\n那唯我独尊的口气……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "嗯？等等，尤蒂尔？\\n说来好像听到过一些传闻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "有个至今为止默默无闻的王子\\n离开王都，并成为了自建国之王以后\\n第一个和多头龙缔结契约的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没错！\\n那个王子就是我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哥哥，巴尔加海姆发生了大规模骚乱，\\n是真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "现在也仍有无辜的人在受到迫害。\\n如果哥哥无暇应对，\\n我们可以帮忙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "骚乱？迫害？\\n没有那种事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我所做的，只不过是“肃清”罢了，\\n清除那些违抗我意之辈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "肃清！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "没错。无需忌惮魔神的力量。\\n它通达神明，\\n能给这个世界带来新的法则。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不能接受这一点的人，\\n唯有肃清。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那就是说巴尔加海姆发生的骚乱，\\n都是你自己干的好事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "时代在改变。\\n亚罗拉斯已经倒下，\\n太古魔神之一建立了新的帝国。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "狄涅尔帝国不是敌人。\\n它超越了对龙的信仰……\\n只是带来我所追求的时代的先驱而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "帝国……不是敌人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，很遗憾，\\n这个人不站在我们这边……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不过，我也没那么执着，\\n想要把信徒都赶尽杀绝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "是那些信徒们自己倒霉。\\n居然逃到了我的目的地——\\n这“红莲废道”之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "目的地……果然，\\n这里面有什么东西吧？到底是什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "那是当然。\\n我想要的只有一个……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "魔神之力。\\n沉眠于此、不属于此世之物……\\n魔神身体的“一部分”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这“红莲废道”正是\\n将其封印的洞窟之一。\\n我一定要亲手得到，这禁忌的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你说是为了得到魔神的力量！？\\n你这家伙！是认真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "当然是认真的。无论是神是龙，\\n还是曾经蹂躏这个世界的魔神，\\n我都无所畏惧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "只要是为了开创人类新纪元，\\n魔神也要为我所用！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "本来历史的前进就必然伴随着牺牲，\\n这次或许也会\\n波及数万人的性命吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哥哥，你在想什么呢！\\n如果，这是真的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "是真的又怎样？你要用你那些\\n弱小的龙和我的契约龙战斗吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "要和烧尽了上百个王国、\\n史上最强的“焰龙”战斗吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "焰龙！？\\n莫非这家伙的契约龙是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你知道些什么吗，穆穆？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "嗯。火龙之中有一头年轻雄龙\\n火力超群，能与我匹敌。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "他名叫——玛斯。\\n如果那头焰龙已经臣服于他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那就在他放出那头危险的龙之前，\\n解决掉他！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "上啊！\\n噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "阁下！危险！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "呜噢！？又是你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我不会让你伤阁下分毫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "这个人现在支援着\\n我们的教会。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "并向我承诺一定会\\n让伊莉雅教变回原来的样子！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "只要跟着他，\\n我们就能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "快清醒过来，沙音！\\n你已经背离神意，迷失自我了！",
